kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到近幾年又9up 貿易戰 反送中 國安法 bno visa好多人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果到今日新樓仲係抽籤先買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二手樓就成交呎價創新高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢西三寶而家都370萬<br />\n<br />\n結論: 樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9604fc4998e4ae60f597d18c0e3afde2e085a0","tid":2456430,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"收住租去補貼移民洗費得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447356922e074ea765610d0ea1cb9e5b851ddbc3","tid":2456430,"uid":258903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3d5f84b52ee4603a1033a00ad01e91646cd00aba","tid":2456430,"uid":231724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"戰狼金管局之前唔係好勁話唔駛理美國既咩?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正當東北三省人口外流衝擊上市公司業績&lt;--呢單又咩事?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"東三省以前係中共發展重鎮<br />\n國有經濟比例非常高<br />\n時至今日變成經濟活力好差<br />\n國有經濟最大問題係唔只自己差<br />\n仲會趕絕/吞併民間資本<br />\n<br />\n所以後生仔唔願留係東三省發展<br />\n人口不斷老化同減少"},{"pid":"732fcbdb66ebaef0dcea7bbc3acf7ba8de95d718","tid":2456430,"uid":169310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6dc7279d850f304c74e4969b72fe9b60982397c","tid":2456430,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score